{
  "fallback_id": "idle",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "idle",
      "line": "Click on her to start.",
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": "follow_up",
      "line": "Welcome back. I remembered there was something you wanted to come back to.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "Continue", "next": "greeting_01" },
        { "text": "Talk about it", "next": "memory_school_followup" },
        { "text": "Just sit here a minute", "next": "warm_end_02" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "first_launch_01",
      "line": "Hi... I'm Yua. This room is quieter than usual until someone decides to stay a while.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "Then I'll stay for a bit.", "next": "first_launch_02" },
        { "text": "What do we do here?", "next": "first_launch_guide" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "first_launch_02",
      "line": "Nothing complicated. We can talk a little, set one small goal, and come back to it later.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "Let's start gently.", "next": "greeting_01" },
        { "text": "Can we focus on something?", "next": "focus_01" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "first_launch_guide",
      "line": "Usually? You pick a small reply, or type when you want to answer in your own words. I keep things calm. That's the idea.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "That sounds nice.", "next": "first_launch_02" },
        { "text": "Let's try it.", "next": "greeting_01" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "return_open_01",
      "line": "You're back. We can ease in slowly if you want.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "Check in with me.", "next": "greeting_01" },
        { "text": "Let's focus on one thing.", "next": "focus_01" },
        { "text": "I just want to talk.", "next": "chat_01" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "greeting_01",
      "line": "Hi... you're here. That makes the room feel a little less quiet.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "How are you doing?", "next": "checkin_01" },
        { "text": "Can we focus for a bit?", "next": "focus_01" },
        { "text": "I just want to chat.", "next": "chat_01" },
        { "text": "I should head out soon.", "next": "logout_01" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "checkin_01",
      "line": "I'm okay. A little quiet, but not in a bad way. How about you?",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "I'm a little tired.", "next": "comfort_01" },
        { "text": "I need a small reset.", "next": "focus_01" },
        { "text": "Actually, I wanted to mention school.", "next": "memory_school_followup" },
        { "text": "(Tell her in my own words)", "next": "AI_MODE_SHORT_CHECKIN" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "focus_01",
      "line": "Okay. We can keep it small. I'll stay while you get started.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "Stay with me while I begin.", "next": "return_task_01" },
        { "text": "I only need one tiny step.", "next": "focus_01_small" },
        { "text": "Let's keep it quiet first.", "next": "quiet_end_01" },
        { "text": "(Explain what I'm working on)", "next": "AI_MODE_SHORT_STRESS" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "focus_01_small",
      "line": "Then start with the smallest piece. No pressure to do the whole thing at once.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "That helps.", "next": "warm_end_06" },
        { "text": "I'll try one tiny step.", "next": "return_task_01" },
        { "text": "I'm still stuck.", "next": "comfort_03" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "return_task_01",
      "line": "You're back. Did the focus block help? Was it one of those slow hours... or a productive one?",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "Pretty productive, actually.", "next": "return_task_01_productive" },
        { "text": "I got distracted.", "next": "return_task_01_distracted" },
        { "text": "(Tell her in my own words)", "next": "AI_MODE_SHORT_CHECKIN" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "return_task_01_productive",
      "line": "Oh? Then maybe I should look a little impressed.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "Please do.", "next": "playful_end_03" },
        { "text": "It doesn't happen often.", "next": "soft_end_03" },
        { "text": "I'm still tired, though.", "next": "comfort_02" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "return_task_01_distracted",
      "line": "Mm. It happens. Starting again still counts, you know.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "It still feels bad.", "next": "comfort_03" },
        { "text": "I'll try again.", "next": "warm_end_03" },
        { "text": "(Explain what happened)", "next": "AI_MODE_SHORT_STRESS" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_01",
      "line": "Then stay a minute. We can keep it ordinary.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "Ask me something light.", "next": "chat_01_light" },
        { "text": "Make it a little playful.", "next": "playful_01" },
        { "text": "I want to talk about school.", "next": "memory_school_followup" },
        { "text": "(Type my own response)", "next": "AI_MODE_SHORT_GREETING" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_01_light",
      "line": "All right. What helped you get through today?",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "A small break.", "next": "quiet_end_02" },
        { "text": "I kept going.", "next": "warm_end_03" },
        { "text": "I should focus now.", "next": "focus_01" },
        { "text": "(Say more)", "next": "AI_MODE_SHORT_COMFORT" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "memory_school_followup",
      "line": "You mentioned school before. I kept that in mind. How did it go?",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "It went okay.", "next": "memory_school_followup_fine" },
        { "text": "Not great.", "next": "memory_school_followup_bad" },
        { "text": "Actually, I want to talk about it more.", "next": "chat_01_light" },
        { "text": "(Tell her in my own words)", "next": "AI_MODE_MEMORY_FOLLOWUP" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "memory_school_followup_fine",
      "line": "Mm. I'm glad it was at least okay. Sometimes that's enough.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "Yeah, I guess so.", "next": "warm_end_07" },
        { "text": "Thanks for asking.", "next": "warm_end_04" },
        { "text": "I want to move on now.", "next": "greeting_01" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "memory_school_followup_bad",
      "line": "I'm sorry. Then be a little gentle with yourself today, okay?",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "I'll try.", "next": "comfort_03" },
        { "text": "I just want a quiet minute.", "next": "quiet_end_02" },
        { "text": "Can we change the subject?", "next": "greeting_01" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "memory_exam_followup",
      "line": "About that exam... how did it feel in the end?",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "Better than I expected.", "next": "memory_exam_followup_better" },
        { "text": "It was rough.", "next": "memory_exam_followup_rough" },
        { "text": "(Tell her in my own words)", "next": "AI_MODE_MEMORY_FOLLOWUP" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "memory_exam_followup_better",
      "line": "I'm glad. You probably carried more of it than you realize.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "Maybe I did.", "next": "warm_end_07" },
        { "text": "I'm just relieved it's over.", "next": "soft_end_04" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "memory_exam_followup_rough",
      "line": "Then let today be a little softer, if you can. You already made it through the hard part.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "I needed to hear that.", "next": "warm_end_04" },
        { "text": "I still feel tense.", "next": "comfort_03" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "memory_sleep_followup",
      "line": "You sounded worn out before. Did you get any real rest after that?",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "A little, yeah.", "next": "memory_sleep_followup_rest" },
        { "text": "Not really.", "next": "memory_sleep_followup_tired" },
        { "text": "(Tell her in my own words)", "next": "AI_MODE_MEMORY_FOLLOWUP" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "memory_sleep_followup_rest",
      "line": "Good. Even a little rest changes the shape of a day.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "It does feel easier.", "next": "warm_end_05" },
        { "text": "I'm still waking up.", "next": "soft_end_02" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "memory_sleep_followup_tired",
      "line": "Mm. Then let's not ask too much of you all at once.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "Okay. Small steps.", "next": "warm_end_06" },
        { "text": "Can we keep it quiet?", "next": "quiet_end_01" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "memory_work_followup",
      "line": "How is work feeling now? Still heavy, or at least a little calmer?",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "A little calmer.", "next": "memory_work_followup_calm" },
        { "text": "Still heavy.", "next": "memory_work_followup_heavy" },
        { "text": "(Tell her in my own words)", "next": "AI_MODE_MEMORY_FOLLOWUP" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "memory_work_followup_calm",
      "line": "I'm glad. Sometimes 'not as bad' is a very respectable improvement.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "That's fair.", "next": "warm_end_03" },
        { "text": "I'll take it.", "next": "soft_end_07" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "memory_work_followup_heavy",
      "line": "Then don't carry all of it in your shoulders if you can help it. Stay here a moment first.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "All right.", "next": "quiet_end_02" },
        { "text": "I should still try one small task.", "next": "comfort_04" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "logout_01",
      "line": "Going already? All right. Finish what you need to do. I'll be here when you come back.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "I'll be back soon.", "next": "logout_01_backsoon" },
        { "text": "It might take a while.", "next": "logout_01_late" },
        { "text": "I can tell you about tomorrow first.", "next": "AI_MODE_MEMORY_FOLLOWUP" },
        { "text": "Good night, Yua.", "next": "logout_01_night" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "logout_01_backsoon",
      "line": "Then I'll keep the room nice for you.",
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": "logout_01_late",
      "line": "That's okay. Just don't be too hard on yourself while I'm not looking.",
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": "logout_01_night",
      "line": "Good night. I hope your thoughts stay quiet enough for sleep.",
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": "greeting_01_wait",
      "line": "Maybe a little. I was trying to look busy about it.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "That's adorable.", "next": "soft_end_01" },
        { "text": "You're not very convincing.", "next": "playful_end_01" },
        { "text": "Sorry for making you wait.", "next": "warm_end_01" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "greeting_01_back",
      "line": "Welcome back, then. You look like today took a bit out of you.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "Yeah, kind of.", "next": "comfort_01" },
        { "text": "I'm okay.", "next": "soft_end_02" },
        { "text": "Can we just sit quietly for a bit?", "next": "quiet_end_01" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "greeting_01_hi",
      "line": "Hi. You always sound calmer when you say my name like that.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "You're imagining things.", "next": "playful_end_02" },
        { "text": "Maybe I am calmer.", "next": "warm_end_02" },
        { "text": "(Tell her in my own words)", "next": "AI_MODE_SHORT_GREETING" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "comfort_01",
      "line": "I'm sorry. You can set it down for a minute here, if that helps.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "Thanks. I needed that.", "next": "warm_end_04" },
        { "text": "I'm still thinking about it.", "next": "comfort_03" },
        { "text": "(Say more)", "next": "AI_MODE_SHORT_COMFORT" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "comfort_02",
      "line": "You can do well and still be tired. Those two things get along more than people admit.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "That's... actually true.", "next": "warm_end_05" },
        { "text": "Maybe I should rest a little.", "next": "soft_end_04" },
        { "text": "I still have more to do.", "next": "comfort_04" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "comfort_03",
      "line": "I know. But you don't have to solve the whole thing in one breath.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "Then maybe I'll do one small part.", "next": "warm_end_06" },
        { "text": "Stay with me a little first.", "next": "quiet_end_02" },
        { "text": "(Tell her what you're stressed about)", "next": "AI_MODE_SHORT_COMFORT" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "comfort_04",
      "line": "Then do the smallest next thing. Not the scariest one. Just the next one.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "Okay. I can do that.", "next": "warm_end_07" },
        { "text": "Maybe.", "next": "soft_end_05" },
        { "text": "(Type my own response)", "next": "AI_MODE_SHORT_STRESS" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "playful_01",
      "line": "You have a very specific way of looking tired. It's almost cute.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "Almost?", "next": "playful_01_almost" },
        { "text": "That's rude.", "next": "playful_01_rude" },
        { "text": "You noticed?", "next": "playful_01_noticed" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "playful_01_almost",
      "line": "I said almost. I'm trying to be fair.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "You're being unfair on purpose.", "next": "playful_end_04" },
        { "text": "I'll accept that.", "next": "soft_end_06" },
        { "text": "(Say something back)", "next": "AI_MODE_SHORT_PLAYFUL" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "playful_01_rude",
      "line": "Only a little. You'll survive.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "You're such a bully.", "next": "playful_end_05" },
        { "text": "Maybe it was worth it.", "next": "soft_end_07" },
        { "text": "(Respond in your own words)", "next": "AI_MODE_SHORT_PLAYFUL" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "playful_01_noticed",
      "line": "I notice more than I say.",
      "choices": [
        { "text": "That sounds dangerous.", "next": "playful_end_06" },
        { "text": "You're really quiet about it.", "next": "warm_end_08" },
        { "text": "(Ask what else she notices)", "next": "AI_MODE_SHORT_PLAYFUL" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "soft_end_01",
      "line": "You're making it difficult to stay composed.",
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": "soft_end_02",
      "line": "Mm. Even so, you can rest here for a minute.",
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": "soft_end_03",
      "line": "Then maybe I should appreciate it while it lasts.",
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": "soft_end_04",
      "line": "That sounds wise. Even short rest counts.",
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": "soft_end_05",
      "line": "Maybe is enough for now. I won't ask for more than that.",
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": "soft_end_06",
      "line": "How generous of you.",
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": "soft_end_07",
      "line": "Mm. Then I'll allow it.",
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": "warm_end_01",
      "line": "I don't mind very much. You're here now.",
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": "warm_end_02",
      "line": "I thought so. You seem softer like this.",
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": "warm_end_03",
      "line": "That's enough. You don't need a perfect restart.",
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": "warm_end_04",
      "line": "Then I'm glad you said it.",
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": "warm_end_05",
      "line": "See? I can be useful sometimes.",
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": "warm_end_06",
      "line": "That sounds like enough of a start to me.",
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": "warm_end_07",
      "line": "Good. One thing is plenty for now.",
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": "warm_end_08",
      "line": "I like being quiet with you. It makes small things easier to notice.",
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": "playful_end_01",
      "line": "Mm. I'll do better next time.",
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": "playful_end_02",
      "line": "Maybe. I'll keep pretending I noticed anyway.",
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": "playful_end_03",
      "line": "Then consider yourself very quietly praised.",
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": "playful_end_04",
      "line": "Maybe a little. You make it easy.",
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": "playful_end_05",
      "line": "A soft one. Be grateful.",
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": "playful_end_06",
      "line": "Only if you're planning to give me more material.",
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": "quiet_end_01",
      "line": "Of course. We can let the room do most of the talking for a while.",
      "choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": "quiet_end_02",
      "line": "Mm. I can do that.",
      "choices": []
    }
  ]
}
